  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个带安全认证的数据处理状态机。系统启动前要先经过OAuth2认证，然后进入空闲状态。核心流程是FETCH获取数据，PARSE解析，然后根据有效性分流到ARB_READ或者直接报错。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，OAuth2作为入口条件连接到IDLE。PARSE之后Valid走ARB_READ，Invalid走ERROR。那ARB_READ和READ是什么关系？看起来还有个授权机制？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "READ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，ARB_READ是仲裁读，获得授权Grant后才进入真正的READ状态。读完之后要仲裁写ARB_WRITE，再授权进入WRITE，最后到CHAIN环节做链式处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把仲裁链画出来了：READ完成触发ARB_WRITE，授权后WRITE执行，然后到CHAIN。CHAIN之后有两个分支对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，CHAIN要判断是不是最后一个数据块。不是的话Next回到FETCH继续拉取，是最后一个就走到COMPLETE，然后发IRQ中断回到IDLE。另外ERROR状态也要能软件清零回到IDLE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，COMPLETE到IDLE标了IRQ sent，ERROR到IDLE标了SW clear。不过FETCH的触发条件我写了Kick-off，PARSE到ARB_READ标了Valid，这些标注对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "ERROR",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "PARSE到ARB_READ的标注应该是Complete，不是Valid。Valid是隐含条件，但状态迁移的触发事件是解析完成。另外FETCH到PARSE也是Complete。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "FETCH"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，PARSE到ARB_READ现在标Complete，FETCH到PARSE也是Complete。整个状态机从Security_OAuth2入口，经过完整的读写仲裁链，支持循环FETCH和错误恢复，结构应该完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "FETCH",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "COMPLETE",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
